660
00:51:05,540 --> 00:51:10,220
Since everything worked out, we are  going to the beach tomorrow morning. Right?

661
00:51:41,470 --> 00:51:45,410
Okay, since everything worked out well.

662
00:51:45,410 --> 00:51:49,520
A glass of champagne is fine.

663
00:51:50,610 --> 00:51:53,290
