665
00:52:01,650 --> 00:52:05,390
Think about whether you have conviction in that moment.

666
00:52:12,450 --> 00:52:18,280
Oh Ha Na. You are convinced enough,  right?

667
00:52:38,340 --> 00:52:41,520
Wow. He's so cool.

668
